page.title: 19A DAY IN A LIFE TIME
page.content: My name is Zenka Geary.I am 9 years old and I will be 10 this year.My favourite work in school is English and swimming. At home in the evening I change my clothes into my shorts and go and call for Samantha Adams and we play on our bikes.Sometimes I like maths and sometimes I dont.I like going on outings at school because they're more exciting.I like snuggling in my bed because its nice and warm.I like watching television especially Superman On Mondays after school I go to gymnastics.I like listening to pop music.I like getting presents for my birthday and for Christmas.I like reading a lot because I think books are exciting. Sept 1985
